cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper is about a 3D object detector using point clouds, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the design of a box prediction network, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on datasets, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) to some extent.
